trans-unit.source: Experimental type system extensions for programs checked with the mypy typechecker.
trans-unit.target: 用mypy typechecker检查程序的实验性类型系统扩展。

trans-unit.source: The “mypy_extensions” module defines experimental extensions to the standard “typing” module that are supported by the mypy typechecker.
trans-unit.target: “ mypy_extensions”模块定义了对mypy typechecker支持的标准“ typing”模块的实验扩展。
